{"type":"article_comment","id":162100,"parentType":"article","parentId":10805,"uid":22816,"contents":"<blockquote>请问关于英国殖民期的反人类行为，我在哪里能找到比较靠谱的资料呢 </blockquote><br>\n<br>\n帝国纵观：<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Historiography_of_the_British_Empire\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Historiography_of_the_British_Empire</a><br>\n以下列一些可以单独找书单的事（贴的不一定是书）：<br>\n<br>\n北美：<a href=\"https://www.liverpoolmuseums.org.uk/ism/resources/origins_chattel_slavery.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">动产奴隶制</a>，<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jul/12/british-history-slavery-buried-scale-revealed\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">跨大西洋奴隶抓/卖</a><br>\n爱尔兰：<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Great-Irish-Potato-Famine-ebook/dp/B0087GK0A4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">土豆饥荒</a><br>\n南非：<a href=\"https://www.halifaxexaminer.ca/featured/white-washing-the-boer-war/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">第二次布尔战争</a><br>\n肯尼亚：<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-12997138\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">茅茅起义</a><br>\n澳大利亚：<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_massacres_of_Indigenous_Australians\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">澳大利亚推广边疆战不完整屠杀事件列表南亚：饥荒，大屠杀</a><br>\n印度/巴基斯坦/孟加拉：<br>\n<a href=\"https://lareviewofbooks.org/article/blighted-by-empire-what-the-british-did-to-india/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://lareviewofbooks.org/article/blighted-by-empire-what-the-british-did-to-india/</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2015/06/29/the-great-divide-books-dalrymple\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">印巴分治</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Timeline_of_major_famines_in_India_during_British_rule\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">南亚殖民时期饥荒列表</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube